# Backend Environment File

Create the following file inside the backend folder.

```id="4h3a6z"
backend/.env
```

Example configuration:

```id="i6v7f1"
CHROMA_DB_PATH=../ingestion/chroma-data
COLLECTION_NAME=documents
```

### Environment Variables

| Variable        | Description                                                          |
| --------------- | -------------------------------------------------------------------- |
| CHROMA_DB_PATH  | Path to the Chroma vector database created by the ingestion pipeline |
| COLLECTION_NAME | Name of the collection storing document embeddings                   |

